   (Message) The `setup_ed25519_key` function calls `torture_change_dir` and
   expects it to succeed, as enforced by the `assert_int_equal(rc, 0);`. If
   `chdir` fails for any reason, `torture_change_dir` returns `-1`, causing this
   assertion to fail. This results in a test abort, setting the error code to 8
